<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Password Reset Link</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .wrapper {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;

        }

        input[type="email"] {
            text-align: center;
            width: 120%;
            padding: 0.8rem;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        button {
            padding: 0.8rem;
            background: rgb(255, 0, 102);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        button:hover {
            background: rgb(162, 0, 65);
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: rgb(255, 0, 102);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Perfect, now that we have that verified...</h2>
    <p>Click the link below to reset your password:</p>
    <a href="<%= resetLink %>" target="_blank">Reset Password</a>
</body>
</html>